---
title: Creamy Dreamy Steak & Mushroom Cavatappi with Scallions & Parmesan
description: If you’re mad for mushrooms, a fan of fungi, or crazy for creminis, this pasta will treat you right. After all ’shrooms are the flavor backbone of this recipe, bringing all those deep, earthy flavors that you know and love. We’ve added springy cavatappi, a dreamy garlic herb sauce, and a sprinkling of Parm. Get ready for this umami bomb to make waves at your dinner table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63064fecce6fdd614906c6c6-f97c652c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-dreamy-steak-mushroom-cavatappi-63064fecce6fdd614906c6c6-87fd88f8.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/creamy-dreamy-steak-and-mushroom-cavatappi-63064fecce6fdd614906c6c6
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 1150 kcal
  fat: 63 g
  saturated fat: 30 g
  carbohydrates: 80 g
  sugar: 10 g
  protein: 60 g
  fiber: 5 g
